<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN"
"http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd">
<html>
<head>
<title>Beta Invite</title>
</head>
<body bgcolor="#eee">
<div id="back" style="background:#eee; padding:10px">
<div id="main" style="font-size:20px; background:#ffffff; padding:6px;">

<div id="start" style="font-weight:bold;">Hello <%=@friend_name%>,</div>



<div id="body" style="padding:16px;">
Your friend, <%=@from_name%>, thought you would benefit from an easier life and decided to invite you to become a beta member of LifeHelpr.com.
<div id="beta" style="background:#CCCCFF; border: 1px solid #aaaaaa; padding:4px; margin-top: 20px; font-weight:bold; font-size:15px">
Your beta code is: <%=@beta_invite.beta_token%><br/><br/>
You can go to: <a href="http://<%=@host%>/register?beta_token=<%=@beta_invite.beta_token%>&email=<%=@beta_invite.email_address%>">http://<%=@host%>/register?beta_token=<%=@beta_invite.beta_token%>&email=<%=@beta_invite.email_address%></a> to sign up.
</div>

<div id="sin" style="font-weight:bold; margin-top:20px;">Sincerly,</div>
<div id="sig" style="font-size:16px; padding-left:6px;">LifeHelpr.com</div>
</div>
<div id="tag" style="font-size:14px; font-weight:bold;"><a style="text-decoration:none;"href="http://lifehelpr.com">lifehelpr.com</a></div>
<div id="footer" style="border-top:2px solid #333; font-size:14px; padding-left: 10px; padding-top:2px;">
<%=@footer['html']%>
</div>
<div id="optout" style="font-size:9px; color:#555555; font-weight:none; padding:10px;">
This email has been sent to <%=@beta_invite.email_address%><br/>
You are receiving this email because you have chosen to receive it.
</div>

</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>